HEADWORD: Pouffe
<hw>Pouffe</hw> }</mhw> <pr>(p⟦oomac⟧f)</pr>,
<pos>n.</pos> <altsp>[Written also <asp>pouff</asp>.]</altsp> <ety>[F.
